      "access_health_technology_mobile_device_assist_healthcare_provider_opt_2": "No",
      "access_health_technology_electronic_device_past_year_health_monitoring": "Other than a tablet or smartphone, have you used an electronic device to monitor or track your health within the last 12 months? Examples include Fitbit, blood glucose meters, and blood pressure monitors.",
