      "access_health_technology_text_message_doctor_past_year_opt_3": "Don't know",
      "sec_next_we_are_going_to_ask_you_some_questi_title": "Next, we are going to ask you some questions about your medical records. Medical records are defined as medical history, such as laboratory test results, clinical notes, and current list of medications.",
